<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link1027233" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=1027233&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F708367-i-m-not-a-scholar-just-looking-for-a-good%2Fanswers%2F1027233-having-read-both-i">flag</a>
</div>
